  "keyFeatures": [
    "Multi-agent deep research with parallel researcher subagents and automated synthesis",
    "Literature review with citation verification and peer-review simulation",
    "Experiment replication on local, Docker, Modal, or RunPod GPU infrastructure",
    "Paper-vs-codebase audit to detect claim mismatches",
    "Source-grounded outputs with inline citations and provenance records",
    "AlphaXiv integration for academic paper search, Q&A, and annotation",
    "Session search and persistent memory across research sessions",
    "Recurring research watches and scheduled background jobs",
    "Skill library installable standalone without the full CLI"
